title: #92Noon! Florio/Lavelle/Tice/Gleeman
description: Twins trade deadline and Vikings football make up most of the Tuesday show! Florio end of first hour, Lavelle from Miami on Twins, former Vikings boss Mike Tice on horses/football/podcasting, and Aaron Gleeman in studio for entire final hour!
